393 |                         component_iter: components_buffer.iter_mut(),
    |                                         ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ `components_buffer` was mutably borrowed here in the previous iteration of the loop
...
400 |         }
    |         - first borrow might be used here, when `components_buffer` is dropped and runs the `Drop` code for type `Vec`

error[E0505]: cannot move out of `components_buffer` because it is borrowed
   --&gt; my_test.rs:398:50
