Task: How to set a Rust module to be public only for doctests?

 <p>I have a public API and a private one. The public API depends on the private one internally. I want to make the private API only public for doctests, so that I can test it directly.</p>
<p>I tried doing it like that:</p>
<pre class="lang-rust prettyprint-override"><code>pub mod public_module {
    use crate::private_module::private_api;

    /// This is a doctest.
