<p>Which is weird because the error is in the doctest which begins on line 20 which is the doctest of the <code>private_module</code> where <code>#[cfg(doctest)]</code> is used (<code>pub</code>), so the flag works, but is also says that the module is defined in line 31 which is the line where <code>#[cfg(not(doctest))]</code> is used.</p>
