<p>So, what gives here? If straightforward (and relatively low LOC) workarounds exist, why can't this simply work out of the box? I suspect there is some lurking risk or fragility with <code>dyn_clone</code>, but I can't find any discussion of it. What are the scenarios where <code>dyn_clone</code> is bad or risky?</p>
